race.comment: TORRENTIAL (4) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (23.05) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Has ability and can bounce back. RAINING WINE (6) turned spotting a big start finishing eighth (18.93) last time in a Grade 5 at Richmond. Form from her last run is proving strong. Bold showing expected. RION EXPRESS (8) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at this track over 400m behind Utmost (23.46) in a Grade 5. Can figure in the finish. DIGGER'S GIRL (3) will be hard to beat with a drop in distance.
